HEADWORD: Gourmand
<hw>Gour"mand</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety> <def>A
greedy or ravenous eater; a glutton. See <er>Gormand</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>That great <qex>gourmand</qex>, fat Apicius.</q> <rj><qau>B.
Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>gourmandize</ent>⟦br⟧
